{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"47g9v","text":"Banders Drums is my channel for drum covers. I grew up loving all kinds of rock and punk music. When I was younger, I played in symphonic band, jazz band, and the orchestra. Over time, I have focused more and more time and energy on playing to the music that I love listening to.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6e6bk","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4njtv","text":"Hardcore and emo bands like Emery and Underoath are my favorite to play to. I also play lots of music that features Travis Barker. Someday, I will write my own music, but for now I will continue posting drum cover videos.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"sc01","text":"Social Channels","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"pl01","text":"Playlists","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"pl02","text":"Drum Covers","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"pl03","text":"Glow Sticks","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi01","text":"Videos","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi02","text":"Blink-182 — All The Small Things","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi03","text":"Blink-182 — Adam's Song","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi04","text":"What happens when your camera isn't mounted very well","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi05","text":"Blink-182 — What's My Age Again","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi06","text":"Blink-182 — Down","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi07","text":"These Green Eyes — Something Perfect","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi08","text":"Box Car Racer — All Systems Go","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi09","text":"Chumbawamba — Tubthumping (Drum Cover)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi10","text":"Queens of the Stone Age — Song for the Dead","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vi11","text":"Underoath — I don't feel very receptive today","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
